                    'The only problem is that HTTPS is not used',
                    'Passwords in URLs appear in: browser history, server access logs, proxy logs, Referer headers sent to third-party scripts, and are visible to anyone looking over the user\'s shoulder. Fix: always use `method="POST"` for credentials, and ensure HTTPS',
