                explanation: '`db.users.find({ age: { $gt: 18 } })` returns a cursor of all matching documents. `db.users.findOne({ email: "a@b.com" })` returns the first match as a single object. `find()` supports query operators (`$gt`, `$in`, `$regex`), projection (include/exclude fields), sort, limit, and skip.',
