                questionText: 'During sprint day 6 of 10, the Product Owner approaches the team with an urgent feature request from a key client — a competitor just launched it and the business impact is high. The feature is estimated at 8 story points. The team\'s sprint commitment is 20 points and they\'ve completed 10 so far. What is the BEST course of action?',
