                questionText: 'Your Next.js App Router page shows a hydration mismatch error: "Warning: Text content did not match. Server: \'12:00 PM\' Client: \'7:00 AM\'". The component renders the current time. The bug disappears in production but appears in development. What is happening and what is the CORRECT fix?',
