                questionText: 'You are deploying a Scikit-learn text classification pipeline containing `TfidfVectorizer` and `SGDClassifier`. The pipeline will receive high-throughput real-time requests. However, you notice that as the vocabulary of new documents grows, prediction latency increases and VRAM/RAM utilization is high. What technique and class should you use to stabilize the feature space and guarantee fixed memory usage?',
                questionType: 'mcq',
